ai_analysis.brief: Short-term bullish momentum on the 5-minute chart with price trading near the upper Bollinger Band and above short-term EMAs.
ai_analysis.detailed: Price is trading above the 20 and 50 EMAs on the 5-minute timeframe with a rising MACD histogram and RSI in the upper-neutral zone, indicating continued upside momentum on pullbacks. Immediate structure shows support around 3820–3850 and resistance into the 3920–3935 area, so a buy-on-pullback with a tight stop beneath the support gives a favorable risk-reward.
